Chelsea have revealed their new third kit for the 2014/15 Premier League season.

It's the first time since Chelsea's 2009/10 double winning season that the west London club have chosen to wear navy blue colours.

The shirt features soundwave-style light blues line, which according to adidas, 'Symbolizes the volume of support from the fans at every away game.'

